summary: So I’m a little late to the party but I finally saw Spiderverse and honestly?
body:
So I’m a little late to the party but I finally saw Spiderverse and honestly?

  1. I see why everyone decided to make a Spider-Man OC now.
  2. Anyone who hasn’t seen that has missed the best animated movie maybe ever
  3. You’ve also missed the best Spider-Man movie ever. Maybe the best superhero movie? At least in the top 5.
  4. Sound track was lit.
  5. I had tears in my eyes after and honestly couldn’t give you a reason why.
  6. It’s a good thing I didn’t see it in theatres because I was literally rocking back and forth in the seat so much with how intense it was I’m surprised the couch didn’t fall over.
  7. You don’t understand if you haven’t seen it it’s the best animated movie ever and it made me want to cry I love it
